	Change quotes to match overall style in NEWS

	loader/xnu: fix memory leak.
	Foound by: Coverity scan.

	util/grub-probe: fix memory leaks.
	Found by: Coverity scan.

	fs/hfsplus: fix memory leak.
	Found by: Coverity scan.

